[02:53.69]	At all times will you have my power alike?
[02:56.87]	Sleeping or waking must I still prevail,
[02:59.91]	Or will you blame and lay the fault on me?
[03:03.09]	Improvident soldiers! had your watch been good,
[03:06.54]	This sudden mischief never could have fall'n.
